      <title>markdown使用说明</title>
      <link href="/2023/020756079.html"/>
      <url>/2023/020756079.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="1、语法块"><a href="#1、语法块" class="headerlink" title="1、语法块"></a>1、语法块</h2><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//代码块语法:</span>```java <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//添加Java语法快</span>```shell <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//添加shell语法块</span></code></pre><h2 id="2、标题"><a href="#2、标题" class="headerlink" title="2、标题"></a>2、标题</h2><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//标题语法</span># 一级标题## 二级标题### 三级标题#### 四级标题##### 五级标题###### 六级标题</code></pre><h2 id="3、字体"><a href="#3、字体" class="headerlink" title="3、字体"></a>3、字体</h2><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//加粗</span><span class="token operator">*</span><span class="token operator">*</span>内容<span class="token operator">*</span><span class="token operator">*</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//代码高亮度显示</span><span class="token operator">==</span>内容<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//删除线</span><span class="token operator">~</span><span class="token operator">~</span>被删除的文字<span class="token operator">~</span><span class="token operator">~</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//斜体</span><span class="token operator">*</span>斜体内容<span class="token operator">*</span></code></pre><p>//下面举例：</p><p>//加粗<br><strong>内容</strong><br>//代码高亮度显示<br>==内容==<br>//删除线<br><del>被删除的文字</del><br>//斜体<br><em>斜体内容</em></p><h2 id="4、引用"><a href="#4、引用" class="headerlink" title="4、引用"></a>4、引用</h2><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//引用语法</span><span class="token operator">></span>诗名：将进酒<span class="token operator">>></span>作者：李白<span class="token operator">>>></span>其他代表作：月下独酌等</code></pre><p>//引用语法</p><blockquote><p>诗名：将进酒</p><blockquote><p>作者：李白</p><blockquote><p>其他代表作：月下独酌等</p></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><h2 id="5、分割线"><a href="#5、分割线" class="headerlink" title="5、分割线"></a>5、分割线</h2><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//分割线1</span><span class="token operator">--</span><span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//分割线2</span><span class="token operator">*</span><span class="token operator">*</span><span class="token operator">*</span>   </code></pre><hr><hr><h2 id="6、图片插入"><a href="#6、图片插入" class="headerlink" title="6、图片插入"></a>6、图片插入</h2><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//在线图片/本地图片</span><span class="token operator">!</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token operator">/</span>image<span class="token operator">/</span>me<span class="token punctuation">.</span>png<span class="token punctuation">)</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//[]里放图片的名字,()里放图片路径</span></code></pre><p><img src="/./markdown%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E/0.jpg" alt="我的照片"></p><h2 id="7、超链接"><a href="#7、超链接" class="headerlink" title="7、超链接"></a>7、超链接</h2><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//超链接语法</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//[]里放链接的名字，()里放链接地址</span></code></pre><p>//超链接语法<br>[我的博客](<a href="https://www.slowfever.xyz/">Slow Fever</a>)</p><h2 id="8、列表"><a href="#8、列表" class="headerlink" title="8、列表"></a>8、列表</h2><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//无序列表</span><span class="token operator">-</span> 目录<span class="token number">1</span><span class="token operator">-</span> 目录<span class="token number">2</span><span class="token operator">-</span> 目录<span class="token number">3</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//有序列表</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">// 1+. +名称</span></code></pre><ul><li><p>目录1</p></li><li><p>目录2</p></li><li><p>目录3</p></li></ul><ol><li><p>首页</p></li><li><p>分类</p></li><li><p>标签</p></li></ol><h2 id="9、表格"><a href="#9、表格" class="headerlink" title="9、表格"></a>9、表格</h2><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java">鼠标右键<span class="token operator">--</span><span class="token operator">></span>插入<span class="token operator">--</span><span class="token operator">></span>表格  </code></pre><table><thead><tr><th>成绩</th><th>数学</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td></td><td>221</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="10、快捷键"><a href="#10、快捷键" class="headerlink" title="10、快捷键"></a>10、快捷键</h2><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//ctrl+shift+1 打开结构图</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//ctrl+/  查看所有内容的源码  </span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
